snippet.title: Neon Genesis Evangelion: Shito Ikusei English Patch First Five Minutes
snippet.description:
Released exclusively for the WonderSwan in 1999, Neon Genesis Evangelion: Shito Ikusei provides a new look into the world in the moments preceding the Third Impact. 

Find out more, including download links here:
https://agtteam.tumblr.com/post/647017217748336640/neon-genesis-evangelion-shito-ikusei-patch

SwanCrystal template used at the end of the video by https://www.deviantart.com/XTCPants
